quran[169]{c,v,t}:
  33,31,"Kala e mooЙ—on Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi, Men yoЙ“iray mo njoЙ“di makko ndin laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—i, MeЙ—en marani mo kadi, arsike tedduЙ—o"
  33,32,"Ko onon yo suddiiЙ“e Annabiijo! On wa'aa wano gooto e suddiiЙ“e Й“en. Si on gomЙ—ii, haray wata on yergin konngol, sakko on mo Гұawu [tuuyo] woni e Й“ernde mun tamЖҙinoo. Wowlon konngol moЖҙЖҙol"
  33,33,"Г‘iiЙ“ee ka cuuЙ—i mon; wata on feГұГұinir cuЙ—aari mon, wano wirtaare majjere adinooЙ“e. Г‘iiЙ“nee Julde nden, totton askal on, Й—oftoЙ—on Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Anndee ko Alla faandii, ko ittanta on e tuuЙ—e, onon yimЙ“e suudu [Annabiijo], O laЙ“Й“inira on laЙ“Й“ingol"
  33,34,"Jantee ko wonaa e janngeede ka cuuЙ—i mon, immorde e Aayeeje Alla, e Sunna. Pellet, Alla laatike NewiiЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  33,35,"Pellet, juulЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e juulЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e Й—oftiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e Й—oftiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e goonguЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e goonguЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e muГұГұiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e muГұГұiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e yankiniiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e yankiniiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e sakkotooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sakkotooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e hoorooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e hoorooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e worЙ“e reenooЙ“e farjuuji mun e rewЙ“e reenooЙ“e farjuuji mun, e worЙ“e jantotooЙ“e Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i Й“en e rewЙ“e jantotooЙ“e Й“en: Alla maranii Й“en, haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  33,36,"Alanaa gomЙ—iЙ—o gorko, wanaa gomЙ—inЙ—o debbo, si Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Гұaawii fiyaaku, nde suЙ“agol e fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on. Kala non yedduЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haray o majjii majjere Й“anngunde"
  33,37,"Janto tuma maakanayno-Й—aa on mo Alla neemini e mun, moЖҙЖҙu-Й—aa e makko: \"Jogitano suddiiЙ—o maa on, hoore-maa, hulaa Alla\", hiЙ—a suuЙ—a e fonndo maa, ko Alla feГұГұinta. HiЙ—a hula yimЙ“e Й“en, kono ko Alla fotu-Й—aa hulude. Tuma Zaydu huntunoo e (suddiiЙ—o) on haaju, Men resin-maa mo, fii wata Й“ittere wonu e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, e (resugol) suddiiЙ“e nodditiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, si Й“en huntii e maЙ“Й“e haaju. Yamiroore Alla nden laatike golleteende"
  33,38,"Feloore alanaa Annabiijo on, e kon ko Alla daginai mo, Й—um ko Гұaawoore Alla e Й“en feЖҙЖҙuЙ“e ado makko. Г‘aawoore Alla nde wonii eЙ“Й“aande hoddiraande"
  33,39,"ЖҒen yottiinooЙ“e nule Alla Й—en, Й“e no hula Mo, Й“e hula goЙ—Й—o goo si wanaa Alla. Alla yonii hasboowo"
  33,40,"Muhammadu wonaali baaba hay goot e worЙ“e mon, ko [o] woni, ko NulaaЙ—o Alla e timmoode AnnabaaЙ“e. Alla laatike AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,41,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, jantoree Alla jantoore Й—uuЙ—unde"
  33,42,Subhinee Mo bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e
  33,43,"Ko Kanko woni yurmeteeЙ—o on, -e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Makko Й“en (du'orana on), - fii no O yaltinira on e niЙ“e faade e annoora. O siforii hinnotooЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  33,44,"Hiwrondiral maЙ“Й“e ngal Гұalnde Й“e hawrata e Makko, ko \"Salaam\" [kisiyee], O maranii Й“e mbarjaari teddundi"
  33,45,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men nulirii ma [fii yo wonu] seediiЙ—o, e wewlinoowo e jertinoowo"
  33,46,"e noddoowo faade e Alla, duЕӢayee Makko; e pitilol jalЙ“ungol"
  33,47,"Wewlinir gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, wonnde no woodani Й“e ka Alla, Й“ural mawnungal"
  33,48,"Wata a Й—ofto heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, Й—uurno (e) lorra maЙ“Й“e kan, fawo-Й—aa e Alla. Sabu Alla yonii ka fawee"
  33,49,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Si resii rewЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, refti on seerii Й“e ado on meemondirde e maЙ“Й“e, haray alanaa on e maЙ“Й“e, edda mo Й“e eddinotoo. Dakmitiree Й“e [njooЙ“a], seeriron Й“e cergal laЙ“aangal"
  33,50,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men daginanii ma suddiiЙ“e maa Й“en Й“e jonnu-Й—aa teЕӢe mun Й“en, e Й“en [horЙ“e] Й“e jeyru-Й—aa Гұaamo maa, e Й“en [dahaaЙ“e] Й“e Alla neldu-maa, e jiwЙ“e bappa maa, e jiwЙ“e yaayiraaЙ“e maa, e jiwЙ“e kaawu-maa, e jiwЙ“e neeniraaЙ“e maa, - Й“en feridunooЙ“e e maa, - e suddiiЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o, si o yeЙ—ii hoore-makko Annabiijo on, si Annabiijo on kadi faandike resugol mo : Й—um ko ko heerani maa, gaanin gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en anndi ko Men farli e maЙ“Й“e kon, e fii suddiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e ko Й“e jeytiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Й—en, fii wata Й“iЙ—teende wonu e maaЙ—a. Alla laatike haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  33,51,"HiЙ—a nennintina on mo yiЙ—u-Й—aa (nennintinnde) e maЙ“Й“e, Й“aЙ—tinaa e maaЙ—a on mo yiЙ—u-Й—aa. E on mo Й—aЙ“Й“u-Й—aa (belagol ka mun) e Й“en Й“e nennitu-Й—aa, bakkaaku woo fawaaki ma. Ko Й—um Й“uri Й“adaade e ko Й“uЙ“Й“inta Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, hara Й“e sunotaako, Й“e weltora kadi ko okku-Й—aa Й“e kon, Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e. Alla no Anndi ko woni e Й“erЙ—e mon. Alla laatike AnnduЙ—o, MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  33,52,"RewЙ“e Й“en dagitantaako ma Й“aawo [Й“ee Й—oo], wanaa nde waЙ—titirtaa Й“e genndiraaЙ“e goo, hay si ЕӢari Й“en Й—on haawnii ma; si wanaa Й“e jeyru-Й—aa Гұaamo maa Й“en. Alla laatike tommbiiЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,53,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Wata on naatu ka cuuЙ—i Annabiijo on, si wanaa hara on nodda e Гұaametee, hara wanaa yo on habbito ko Й“enndi ka makko. Kono si on noddaa ma, naatee. Si on Гұaamii, sentee, hara on Й—aЙ“Й“aali haala. Anndon Й—um mooЙ—on, hino lorraynoo Annabiijo on, kono o hersa (haalannde) on, Alla non Й—alataa [yamirde] goonga. Si on lanndoto (suddiiЙ“e makko) Й“en haaju, lanndoree Й“e Й“aawo wirngallo: ko Й—um mooЙ—on, Й“uri laaЙ“annde Й“erЙ—e mon e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Haananaa on nde lorroton NulaaЙ—o Alla on, wanaa nde resoton suddiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Й“aawo makko, poomaa; pellet, waЙ—ugol mon Й—um, wonii ko mawni ka Alla"
  33,54,"Si on feГұГұinii huunde, maa on suuЙ—ii nde, pellet, Alla laatike annduЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,55,"Bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa kadi Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa e Й“iЙ—Й“e banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa e Й“iЙ—Й“e miГұГұiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en, wanaa e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa e Й“en Й“e Й“e jeyiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e. Hulee Alla (yo suddiiЙ“e). Pellet, Alla siforii seediiЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,56,"Pellet, Alla e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, hiЙ“e du'anaade Annabiijo on; ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, juulee e makko, toranoЙ—on [Mo] kisiyee"
  33,57,"Pellet, Й“en lorrooЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Alla huЙ—ii Й“en aduna e laakara, O hebilanii Й“e kadi lepte hoynooje"
  33,58,"ЖҒen kadi lorrooЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e hoore ko Й“e faggitaaki, gomЙ—ii Й“e ronndike fenaande e bakkaatu Й“annguЙ—o"
  33,59,"Ko an yo Annabiijo! Maakan suddiiЙ“e maa Й“en, e jiwЙ“e maa Й“en, e genndiraaЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, nde Й“e joltinta e maЙ“Й“e, wutteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in: ko Й—um Й“urata Й“aЙ—taade, nde Й“e annditetee, hara Й“e torraaka. Alla laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  33,60,"Pellet, si naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en haЙ—itaaki, e Й“en Й“e Гұawu (sikkitaare) woni e Й“erЙ—e mun, e fena-fenta'en ka saare Madiina, ma Men wurtite e maЙ“Й“e, refi Й“e kawtirtaa e maaЙ—a ton, si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  33,61,"Ko huЙ—aa Й“e. Kala ka Й“e tawaa, ko Й“e nanngetee Й“e, Й“e waree wargol"
  33,62,"ЖҠum ko sunna Alla e Й“en wulinooЙ“e ko adii. A heЙ“antaa laawol (sunna) Alla ngol, battiigu"
  33,63,"YimЙ“e Й“en o lanndo maa fii Darngal. Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal daragol maggal, ko ka Alla woni\". E ko anndin maa, wonnde no hasii hara Darngal ngal Й“adike"
  33,64,"Pellet, Alla huЙ—ii heeferЙ“e Й“en, O kammbiranii Й“e kadi dulboowe"
  33,65,"ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton poomaa. ЖҒe heЙ“ataa giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  33,66,"Г‘alnde geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en waylitetee ka Yiite, Й“e wi'ay: \"Ee jalla amen! Hara men Й—oftino Alla, men Й—oftii NulaaЙ—o on"
  33,67,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, Menen men Й—ofti hooreeЙ“e amen e mawЙ“e amen, Й“e majjini men e laawol ngol"
  33,68,"Joomi amen, tottu Й“e cowanlle Й—iЙ—i e lepte Й—en, huЙ—aa Й“e kuddi mawndi"
  33,69,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e! Wata on wa'u wa Й“en lorrunooЙ“e Muusaa, Alla woЙ—Й—ini mo e ko Й“e wi'i kon, tawde o wonii tedduЙ—o ka Alla"
  33,70,"Ko on yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e! Hulee Alla, wowlon konngol feewungol"
  33,71,"[Si on waЙ—ii Й—um], O moЖҙЖҙinanay on golle mon, O haforana on junuubi mon. Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haray o maliraama maloore mawnde"
  33,72,"Men weeЙ“itii hoolaare nden e dow kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin e pelle Й—en, Й—i haЙ—itii ronndagol nde, Й—i huli (battane) majji, neЙ—Й—o on kan ronndii nde; tawde pellet, o wonii Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o-tooГұude [hoore-mun], majjaaЙ—o [battane Й—um]"
  33,73,"[NeЙ—Й—o on ronndiraama Й—um], no Alla leptira naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e sirkooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sirkooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e (no) Alla jaЙ“irana gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en tuububuyee. Alla laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  34,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On jeyЙ—o kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Hino woodani Mo kadi yettoore ka laakara. Ko Kanko woni Г‘eeГұo, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  34,2,"Himo anndi ko naatata ka leydi, e ko yaltata e mayri, ko jippotoo iwra ka kammu e ko Жҙawata e maggu. Ko Kanko woni Hinnotoo, Haforoowo"
  34,3,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"Darngal ngal arataa men\". Maaku: \"aa'a! Mi woondirii Joomi am! pellet, ko aray e mon. [Joomi ma] ko AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i. Huunde wirnanaaki Mo, ko fotata e abbere jarra, woni ka kammuuli maa ka leydi. Wanaa ko Й“uri Й—um fanЙ—ude, wanaa ko Й“uri Й—um mawnude, si wanaa no e deftere feГұГұinnde"
  34,4,"Fii yo O yoЙ“oy Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani Й“e haforaneede, e arsike tedduЙ—o"
  34,5,"ЖҒen non yaccii Й“e e bonnitugol Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte, immorde e Й“urЙ—e muusude"
  34,6,"ЖҒen okkaaЙ“e ganndal hino yi'ira jippiniraande nden e maaЙ—a, immorde ka Joomi maa, ko kayre woni goonga, hinde fewnira e laawol FooluЙ—o, YettiniiЙ—o On"
  34,7,"YedduЙ“e Й“en kadi wi'i: \"On accay men tinndina on fii gorko, mo no humpita on, wonnde si on muncitaama kala muncitannde, on wontoyay e tagu hesu"
  34,8,"O fefindi fenaande e hoore Alla? Kaa hara ko jinna nanngi mo? Si ko woni, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara on, Й“e wonii e lepte e majjere woЙ—Й—iinde (goonga)"
  34,9,"E Й“ee yi'aali ko woni yeeso maaЙ“e e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Si Men muuyiino, Men munnirayno Й“e leydi ndin, maa Men fukkina e maЙ“Й“e taЖҙontine (lepte), immorde ka kammu. Wonii e Й—um, maande, wonannde kala jeyaaЙ—o ruttotooЙ—o (e Joomi mun)"
  34,10,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Daawuuda Й“ural, immorde e Amen. [Men wi'i]: \"Ko onon pelle e colli, subbunhinodee e makko. Men newinani mo (tafugol) njamndi ndin"
  34,11,"(Men wi'ani mo wonnde): \"Gollu wutteeji njamndi, eЙ“Й“aa ka tafoodi. Gollon golle moЖҙЖҙe, pellet, ko Mi ReenuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  34,12,"(Men eltani kadi) Sulaymaana henndu ndun: dawol mayru ko yeru (yaadu) lewru, kirndol mayru kadi ko yeru (yaadu) lewu. Men honcinani mo Й“unndu sila (kire). Hino jinnaaji Й—in, golliraynooЙ—i yeeso makko, e duЕӢayee Joomi Makko. Kala ooГұiingii e majji, gaay e yamiroore Amen nden, Men meeЙ—ina ngii lepte dulЙ“oowe ngen"
  34,13,"HiЙ—i gollana mo ko o faalaa: gila e tataaji, e nanndollaaji, e looЙ—e wa'uЙ—e wa beeli, e payanЙ—e feЕӢiiЙ—e. \"Gollee, onon Й“eynguure Daawuuda, yetton (Alla)\", fanЙ—ii e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en, yettoowo (Lam)"
  34,14,"Nde Men Гұaawunoo e makko maayde nden, anndinaali Й—i fii maayde makko nden, si wanaa gannguuji leydi(mooЖҙu) Й—in, hino Гұaama tuggordu makko ndun. Nde o fukkinoo, feeГұani jinnaaji Й—in, wonnde si Й—i anndunoo ko wirnii, Й—i ГұiiЙ“ataano e lepte [jeyaagu] hoynooje"
  34,15,"GomЙ—ii wonaniino yimЙ“e Saba'i Й“en e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in, maande; gese Й—iЙ—i ka bannge Гұaamo e ka nano. (Men wi'ani Й“e): \"Г‘aamee e arsike Joomi mon, yetton Mo. Leydi ndin ko laaЙ“undi, e Joomiraawo Haforoowo"
  34,16,"(Kono) Й“e Й—uunii. Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e ndiyam waame, Men waЙ—titani Й“e gese maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й—iЙ—i, gese (goo) Й—iЙ—i, marЙ—e Гұaametee haaЙ—uЙ—o, e (leЙ—Й—e) duЙ“Й“eeje, e huunde e jaaЙ“e seeЙ—aaje"
  34,17,"Ngool (yaggingol), Men yoЙ“irЙ“e ko Й“e yeddi kon. E hara Men yoЙ“ay si wanaa yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  34,18,"Men waЙ—i hakkune maЙ“Й“e e koЙ—ooli Й—i Men waЙ—i barki e mun Й—in, koЙ—ooli feeГұondirЙ—i, Men eЙ“Й“i e majji yaadu. (Men wi'ani Й“e): \"Yehee ton jemmaaji e Гұalormaaji, ko on hooliiЙ“e"
  34,19,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, woЙ—Й—indir hakkunde yaaduuji amen\", Й“e tooГұi ko'e maЙ“Й“e, Men waЙ—ti fillitee Й“e fii mun, Men senndindiri Й“e hattirde e senndirgol. Pellet, wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde kala heewuЙ—o muГұal, yettoowo (neema)"
  34,20,"GomЙ—ii Ibuliisa goonginii jikke mun Й—en e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe jokki mo, si wanaa fedde e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  34,21,"E doole alanaa mo e dow maЙ“Й“e, cemmbe (wurtugol), si wanaa tun, ko fii no Men anndira on gomЙ—inЙ—o laakara e on wonЙ—o e sikke fii mun. Joomi maa non, e dow kala huunde, ko O reenuЙ—o"
  34,22,"Maaku: \"Noddee Й—in Й—i Й—aynitorЙ—on [ reweteeЙ—i] gaanin Alla. ЖҠi jeyaa hay yeru abbere jarra, ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi. Alanaa Й—i e Й—in (kammuuli e leydi ndin) kafidaaЙ—o (geЙ“al), alanaa Mo e Й—in, hay wallondirteeЙ—o"
  34,23,"Tefoore woo nafataa ka Makko, si wanaa on Mo O duЕӢanii. Haa si Й—enЖҙere nden yaltinaama e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'a: \"Ko honЙ—um Joomi mon daali?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"Ko goonga kan; ko Kanko woni ToowuЙ—o, MawЙ—o On"
  34,24,"Maaku: \"Kon hombo woni arsikiroowo on ka kammuuli e ka leydi?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla. Ko si ko menen maa si ko onon, woni e peewal maa e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  34,25,"Maaku: \"On lamnditoytaake fii ko men bonni, menen kadi men lamnditoytaake fii ko huuwoton"
  34,26,"Maaku: \"Joomi men renndinoyay en, refti O Гұaawira hakkunde men goonga; Ko Kanko woni Г‘aawoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  34,27,"Maaku: \"Hollee lam Й—in Й—i waЙ—tidu-Й—on e Makko kafidiiЙ—i. Wanaa non woniri! Si ko woni, ko Kanko woni Alla FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o On"
  34,28,"Men nuliraali ma, si wanaa e yimЙ“e Й“en fow: wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e anndaa"
  34,29,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  34,30,"Maaku: \"Hino woodani on fodoore, nde o nennitantaake e mayre fotde saa'i, on ardintinantaake nde kadi"
  34,31,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—intaa ndee Alqur'aanaare muk, wanaa nden adiinde nde\". Sinno a tinayno tuma nde tooГұuЙ“e Й“en darnetee ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hara yoga maЙ“Й“e no rutta yoga konngol, lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en wi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“en: \"Si wanaano onon nun, men wonayno gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  34,32,"TownitinooЙ“e Й“en wi'ani lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en: \"E ko menen falinoo on e peewal Й“aawo ngal arde e mon? Si ko woni, on woniino bomЙ“e"
  34,33,"Lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en kadi wi'ani townitinooЙ“e Й“en: \"Si ko woni, ko pewje (mon) jemma e Гұalorma, tuma yamiraynoЙ—on men yo men yeddu Alla, men waЙ—ana Mo fotondirЙ—i\". ЖҒe suuЙ—i ninse Й—en, nde Й“e yi'unoo lepte Й—en. Men waЙ—i kolombooje e daaЙ—e Й“en yedduЙ“e. Hara Й“e yoЙ“itete si wanaa ko Й“e huuwaynoo kon"
  34,34,"Men nulaali jertinoowo e yimЙ“e saare, si wanaa neeminaaЙ“e mayre Й“en wi'ay: \"Menen ko men yedduЙ“e ko nulidaЙ—on kon"
  34,35,"ЖҒe wi'i kadi: \"Ko menen Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude jawle e Й“iЙ“Й“e, men wonaali kadi lepteteeЙ“e"
  34,36,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am hino weertana arsike on, mo O muuyi, O Й“illini (mo O muuyi). Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e anndaa"
  34,37,"Wanaa jawle mon, wanaa jiidi mon woni ko Й“aЙ—tinirta on ka Amen Й“adal. Si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe; Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di sowaande, sabu ko Й“e golli kon, kamЙ“e ka soorooji, ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e"
  34,38,"ЖҒen yaccotooЙ“e e ronkingol (yimЙ“e Й“en) e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, ka ka nder lepte woni ko Й“e tawnoytee"
  34,39,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am hino weertana arsike on, mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O Й“illini mo (O muuyi e maЙ“Й“e). Kala non ko wintiЙ—on e huunde, Kanko O lontinay nde. Ko Kanko woni MoЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo"
  34,40,"Г‘alnde O mooЙ“tindiroyta Й“e dendaangal, refti O daalana Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en: \"E ko Й“ee Й—oo (yimЙ“e) rewaynoo on"
  34,41,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Senayee woodanii Ma! Ko An woni giЙ—o amen gaanin maЙ“Й“e. Toode ko jinnaaji Й—in Й“e rewaynoo, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й—in (jinnaaji) gomЙ—ini"
  34,42,"Hannde non, yoga mon waawanaa yoga nafa wanaa lorra. Men wi'anoya Й“en tooГұuЙ“e: \"MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge fennaynoЙ—on fii mun"
  34,43,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—en janngaamma e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a: \"Oo wonaali, si wanaa gorko faalaaЙ—o falagol on e ko baabiraaЙ“e mon rewayno rewaynoo\". ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ndee (AlqurвҖҷaanaare) wonaali, si wanaa fenaande fefindaande\". YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ani goonga kan nde ka arunoo e maЙ“Й“e: \"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu Й“anngu ngu"
  34,44,"Men addanaali Й“ee, defte Й—e Й“e janngata. Men meeЙ—aali nulude e maЙ“Й“e, jertinoowo ado maa"
  34,45,"AdinooЙ“e Й“e Й“en [kadi] fenniino (nulaaЙ“e mun). [YimЙ“e maa Й“en] yottaaki sappaЙ“al ko Men okkunoo Й“en kon. ЖҒen fenni NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, taskii no lepte Am Й—en wa'unoo"
  34,46,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi waajorta on, ko (huunde) wootere: \"Ko nde daroranton Alla Й—iЙ—o Й—iЙ—o e gooto gooto, refti miijitoЙ—on. (Anndon) wondiiЙ—o mon on aldaa e jinna: O wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo on, e ko woni yeeso (mon), e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  34,47,"Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di, Й—um ko fii mon. NjoЙ“di am ndin wonaali, si wanaa ka Alla. Kanko Ko O SeediiЙ—o e kala huunde"
  34,48,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am ko werlortooЙ—o [meere nden, hujjaaji] goonga kan, timminЙ—o anndugol wirniiЙ—i"
  34,49,"Maaku: \"Goonga kan arii [Iislaamu on], meere [keeferaaku] ngun alaa ka feeГұa, kadi, nde ruttotaako"
  34,50,"Maaku: \"Si mi majjii, haray ko hoore-am mi majjani; si mi feewii kadi, ko sabu ko sabu ko Joomi am wahayini e am kon, tawde pellet, ko O Nanoowo, ЖҒadiiЙ—o"
  34,51,"Sinno a tinayno, tuma nde Й“e Й—enyii, - laaworde alanaa (Й“e), - Й“e nanngiree e nokkuure Й“adiinde"
  34,52,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Men gomЙ—inii [Darngal] ngal\", e ko honno gomЙ—inal woonirani Й“e e nokku woЙ—Й—uЙ—o"
  34,53,"Hara non Й“e yeddiino nde ko adii, hiЙ“e werlora ko wirnii e nokku woЙ—Й—uЙ—o"
  34,54,"Heedee hakkunde e ko Й“e tuuyetee, wano golliranoo e nanndo maЙ“Й“e ko adii, tawde Й“e woniino e sikke cikkiniiЙ—a"
  35,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, WaЙ—uЙ—o Malaa'ika'en nulaaЙ“e, marЙ“e gabitanji(bibje) Й—i Й—iЙ—i, Й—i tati e nayi. Himo Й“eyda ko O muuyi e tagu Makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yimЙ“e Й“en, jogitotooЙ—o nde alaa; kala kadi ko O jogitii, accitoowo Й—um alaa Й“aawo (jogitagol) Makko. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  35,3,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! jantee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko! E ko honno yiilirteЙ—on [e kaa goonga]"
  35,4,"Si Й“e fennii ma, pellet NulaaЙ“e (goo) fennanooma ado maa. Ko faade e Alla, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in"
  35,5,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Anndee pellet fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wata nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata (seytaane) hodoowo on hodu on e fii Alla"
  35,6,"Pellet, seytaane ko gaГұo wonani on. Haray jogitoree mo gaГұo. Anndee ko o noddirta fedde makko nden, ko no Й“e jeydiree e yimЙ“e dulЙ“oowe ngen"
  35,7,"Hino woodani yedduЙ“e Й“en, lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e. ЖҒeya gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hino woodani Й“e haforaneede e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  35,8,"E ko on cuЙ—inanaaЙ—o golle mun bonЙ—e, hara himo yi'a Й—e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—e? - Tawde pellet, Alla no majjina on Mo O muuyi, O fewna Mo O muuyi. Wata a tampinir hoore-maa, sunagol fii maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko Й“e woni huuwude"
  35,9,"Ko Alla woni wurtuЙ—o keneeli Й—in, Й—i sogga duule, Men yarnira Й—um leydi yoorundi; Men wuurnitira Й—um leydi ndin, Й“aawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano non ummital ngal"
  35,10,"Kala tawЙ—o ko teddungal faalaa (yo o Й—aЙ“Й“ir Alla), tawde ko Alla jeyi teddungal ngal fow: ko ka Makko woni ko konngol laaЙ“ungol Жҙawata, golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en Й“amta ngol. ЖҒen fewjooЙ“e boneeji, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e. Pewje Й“en Й—en, ko bonay Й—e"
  35,11,"Ko Alla tagiri on e mbulbuldi, refti e toЙ“Й“ere (maniiyu), refti O waЙ—i on nooneeji. Deyel saawataa, ngel lelnataa kadi, si wanaa e anndal Makko. WuurnaaЙ—o wuurnetaake, Й—uytetaake kadi e nguurndam makko, si wanaa no e deftere. Pellet, Й—um ko newanii Й—um Alla"
  35,12,"Maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i fotataa: [Ndiyam] goo Й—oo Й—am, ko welЙ—am, laaЙ“ungo, newiingo njaram mun, ngoo Й—aa, ko lanЙ—am haaЙ—uЙ—am. HiЙ—on Гұaama e kala majjam, teewu keccu, hiЙ—on yaltina kadi hen, cuЙ—aari ndi Й“oornotoЙ—on. HiЙ—a yi'a laaЙ—e Й—en no awja e maggo, fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“iron e Й“ural Makko. Belajoo on yettay [Mo]"
  35,13,"Himo naada jemma on e der Гұalorma on, O naada Гұalorma on e nder jemma on. O elti kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun. Kala mun no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Ko On mooЙ—on woni Alla, Joomi mon: Ko Kanko Laamu woodani. ЖҠiya Й—i noddoton gaanin Makko, Й—i jeytaa yeru gorol tamara"
  35,14,"Si on noddu Й—i, Й—i nanataa noddaandu mon; hay si Й—i nanoy, Й—i jaabitotaako on. Г‘alnde Darngal, Й—i yeddoyay sirku mon on. Alaa habroowo ma, wano HumpitiiЙ—o On"
  35,15,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, ko onon woni hatonjimЙ“e e Alla Й“en, Alla kan, ko Kanko woni Galo YettiniiЙ—o On"
  35,16,"Si O yiЙ—ii, O naЙ“a on, O adda tagu hesu"
  35,17,ЖҠum wonaali sattuЙ—um ka Alla
  35,18,"Wonki ronndotaako doЕӢgal wonkii goo. Hay si teddiraaki [junuubi] kin noddii e ronndaneede, ki ronndantaake hay huunde, hay si ko Й“adondiraaЙ—o Anndu ko jertintaa [nana waaju], ko Й“en hulirooЙ“e Joomi mun ka wirnii, Й“e ГұiiЙ“i e Julde. Kala on laЙ“Й“iniiЙ—o, haray ko hoore makko o woni laЙ“Й“inanaade. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  35,19,BunЙ—o e yi'oowo fotataa
  35,20,wanaa niЙ“e Й—en e ndaygu ngun
  35,21,wanaa Й—owdi ndin e henndu wulndu ndun
  35,22,"Wanaa kadi wuurЙ“e Й“en fotata e maayЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla no nanina on Mo O muuyani. Wanaa an [NulaaЙ—o], woni naninoowo, wonЙ“e ka genaale Й“en"
  35,23,"An a wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo"
  35,24,"Pellet, Men nulirii ma goonga, ko a wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wanaa jertinoowo feЖҙЖҙii e maЙ“Й“e"
  35,25,"Si Й“e fennii ma, hari adinooЙ“e Й“e Й“en fenniino (NulaaЙ“e mun), fewndo Й“en NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e addannoo Й“anngannduyeeji, e ЖҠeri e Deftere ndayginoore"
  35,26,Refti nanngitir mi yedduЙ“e Й“en (halakuyee). Taskii no lepte An Й—en waЙ—tinirnoo
  35,27,"E a tinaali wonnde Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Men fuЙ—iniri Й—am dimЙ—e seertuЙ—e noone. Hino ka pelle, Й—ate daneeje e boЙ—eeje seertyuЙ—e noone, e pete Й“aleeje"
  35,28,"Hino e yimЙ“e Й“en, e daabeeji Й—in, e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, Й—i nooneeji mun kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko hulata Alla e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, ko annduЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o, Haforoowo"
  35,29,"ЖҒen janngooЙ“e Deftere Alla nden, Й“e ГұiiЙ“i e julde, Й“e nafqii ko Men arsiki Й“e kon gunndoo e kene, hiЙ“e jortii njulaaku ngu sontataa"
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana Й“e njoЙ“diiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O Й“eyda Й“e e Й“ural Makko ngal. Kanko, ko O Haforoowo, Annditanoowo [on]"
  35,31,"Kon ko Men wahayini e maaЙ—a e Deftere nden, ko Й—um woni goonga, gomЙ—inde e Й—en wonЙ—e yeeso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko HumpitiiЙ—o RentuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  35,32,"Refti Men ronini Deftere nden, Й“en Й“e Men suЙ“ii e jeyaaЙ“e Amen. Hino e maЙ“Й“e tooГұuЙ“e hoore-mun, hino e maЙ“Й“e hakindinЙ—o, hino e maЙ“Й“e foolondirooЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙereeji, duЕӢayee Alla; ko Й—um woni Й“ural mawnungal ngal"
  35,33,"Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—i naatata e mun, hara hiЙ“e cuЙ—iree ton, jawe kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise e luвҖҷu-luвҖҷu; comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in ton, ko sooyi"
  35,34,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ittanЙ—o en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko Haforoowo, WarjotooЙ—o"
  35,35,"On weernirЙ—o en Й“ural Makko ngal, e galle ГұiiЙ“al, tampere (woo) heЙ“ataa en ton, wanaa ronkere heЙ“ata en ton"
  35,36,"YedduЙ“e Й“en kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani Й“en; maayde Гұaawetaake e maЙ“Й“e, sakko Й“e maaya, Й“e hoynantaake kadi lepte magge Й—en. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“itirta kala yedduЙ—o"
  35,37,"Hara hiЙ“e ooloo nder ton [Й“e wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, yaltin men; men golla moЖҙЖҙere, hara wonah ko men gollaynoo kon\". [O jaaboo Й“e]: \"E men wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotooЙ—o waajitoranoo e mun? Jertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa meeЙ—ee, sabu faabo alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko O AnnduЙ—o ko suuЙ—ii e Й“erЙ—e"
  35,39,"Ko Kanko woni waЙ—uЙ—o on lontiiЙ“e ka leydi. Kala yedduЙ—o, ko e makko lorra geddi makko yantata. Yeddugol heeferЙ“e Й“en, Й“eydataa Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa tikkere. Yeddugol Й“eydataa heeferЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa hayrere"
  35,40,"Maaku: \"E on yi'ii rendiiЙ—i mon rewoton gaanin Alla Й—in? Hollee lam ko Й—i tagi ka leydi. Kaa hiЙ—i mari geЙ“al e [tagugol] kammuuli Й—in? Kaa Men addan Й“e Deftere, nde Й“e woni e Й“anndannduyee mun? Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en alaa e fodude yoga maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa hodo"
  35,41,"Pellet, ko Alla jogitii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, fii wata Й—i dirtu. Hay si Й—i dirtayno, hay gooto jogitotaako Й—i e Й“aawo Makko. O laatike MuГұГұiiЙ—o, Haforoowo"
  35,42,"ЖҒe woodndiri Alla, hattirde e goondooje maЙ“Й“e, wonnde si jertinoowo arii e maЙ“Й“e, pellet, Й“e wonay Й“urЙ“e feewude wootere e mofte Й—en. Nde jertinoowo non arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um Й“eydaali Й“e, si wanaa woЙ—Й—itagol"
  35,43,"[ЖҒe waЙ—iri Й—um] mawnintinaare ka keydi, e pewje Й“enЙ—e. Pewje bonЙ—e Й—en non huuЙ“itataa, si wanaa jom-mun'en. Hara hiЙ“e sabbitii, si wanaa sunna (Alla) on e adinooЙ“e Й“en? A heЙ“antaa sunna Alla on battiigu, a heЙ“antaa sunna Alla waylirЙ—um"
  35,44,"E Й“ee yiilaaki ka leydi, Й“e taskoo ko honno battane adinooЙ“e Й“en wonirnoo? Hari no Й“uri Й“e tiiЙ—ude doole. Alla siforaali wonnde goЙ—Й—um no ronkina Mo ka kammuuli maa ka leydi. Tawde pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o, HattanЙ—o"
  35,45,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yimЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e faggitorii kon, O accataano ruugayngel e dow mayri. Ko woni tun, Himo nennitana Й“e haa e lajal anndaa ngal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal hewtii, [O nanngay Й“e], tawde pellet, Alla ko ReenuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  36,1,Yaa-Siin
  36,2,Mi woondirii Al*ur'aana ГұeГұaande nden
  36,3,"Pellet, an (NulaaЙ—o), ko a jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  36,4,E dow laawol focciingol
  36,5,"Jippinannde On FooluЙ—o, Hinnotoo"
  36,6,"Fii yo a jertinir nde yimЙ“e, Й“e baabiraaЙ“e mun jertinanooka: Й“en ko welsindiiЙ“e"
  36,7,"GomЙ—ii konngol [lepte] jojjii e ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e; Й“en Й—on gomЙ—intaa"
  36,8,"Menen Men waЙ—ii ka daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e kolommbooje, Й—en ko yottiiЙ—e ka bokkuЙ—e; hara ko Й“e ЕӢalliniiЙ“e"
  36,9,"Men waЙ—i yeeso maЙ“Й“e heedo, Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e kadi heedo, Men hippi Й“e (gite Й—en); waЙ—ti Й“e yi'ataa [goonga]"
  36,10,"Hino fota e maЙ“Й“e, foti a jertini Й“e, maa a jertinaali Й“e; Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  36,11,"Anndu ko jertintaa (jaЙ“a), ko on jokkuЙ—o Jantoore (Alqur'aana) nden, o huli Jom-Yurmeende On ka wirnii. Wewlinir mo haforaneede e mbarjaari teddundi"
  36,12,"Ko Menen woni wuurnitooЙ“e maayЙ“e Й“en, Men winnda ko Й“e ardini e batteeji maЙ“Й“e. Kala huunde, MeЙ—en mofti nde e deftere Й“anngunde"
  36,13,"Piyan-Й“e misal, fii yimЙ“e saare, tuma nde NulaaЙ“e arunoo Й“e"
  36,14,"Nde Men nulunoo e maЙ“Й“e, [NulaaЙ“e] Й—iЙ—o, Й“e fenni Й“en, Men sammbiniri Й“en, tataЙ“o, Й“e wi'i: \"Menen, ko men NulaaЙ“e e mo'on"
  36,15,"[YimЙ“e saare nden] wi'i: \"On wonaali, si wanaa ko on Й“anndinke wano menen. Jom-hinaranke On jippinaali hay huunde, on wonaali, si wanaa ko on fenooЙ“e"
  36,16,"[NulaaЙ“e Й“en] wi'i: \"Joomi amen no anndi pellet, ko men NulaaЙ“e e mo'on"
  36,17,"Fawaaki men non, si wanaa yottingol Й“anngina"
  36,18,"[YimЙ“e saare nden] wi'iti: \"Men hiitori on kataa. Si tawii non on haЙ—itaaki, ma men fiЙ—u on, lepte muusuЙ—e kadi memira on immorde e amen"
  36,19,"[NulaaЙ“e Й“en kadi] wi'iti: \"Kiite mon Й—in, hiЙ—on wonndi e mun. Ko si on waajaama (hiitinoЙ—on)? Tigi on, ko on yimЙ“e fantinooЙ“e"
  36,20,"Gorko iwri ka Й“uri woЙ—Й—ude e saare nden, o ari himo yaccoo, o wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, kori jokkee NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  36,21,"jokkee Й“en Й“e lamndotaako on njoЙ“di, Й“en ko fewnaaЙ“e"
  36,22,E ko haЙ—ata lam rewugol On taguЙ—o Lam? Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon
  36,23,"E mi jogtoto reweteeЙ—i gaanin Makko? Si Jom-yurmeende On muuyanii lam lorra, tefoore majji duncantaali lam hay huunde, Й—i dЙ—andataa lam kadi"
  36,24,"Haray min ontuma, mi wonii e majjere Й“anngunde"
  36,25,"Min on, mi gomЙ—inii Joomi mon, nananee lam"
